      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic restoration. The engine is difficult to start and has a persistent knock, while the transmission shifts roughly. The body shows significant rust and several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. It is best suited as a major project car or for parts.",
